Create Metric Filter in CloudWatch Logs
- Log groups
- Select HttpAccessLogs
- Select Action
- Create metric filter : filter patter [ip, id, user, timestamp, request, status_code=404, size] | select log data to test
- Next
- Filter name, metrics namespace, metric name, metric value, create metric

Create Alarm Using Filter
- select filter
- create alarm
-- Period, Greaterthan, threshold
- Next
- Create new topic (SNS topic)
- enter email
